comment._content: Judge Edward Swann, democratic candidate for District Attorney, New York county in 1915 (see The sun., October 03, 1915, FOURTH SECTION PICTORIAL MAGAZINE, Image 29) and obviously elected, see The Day book., May 25, 1916, NOON EDITION, Image 10: HE'S PROSECUTOR IN WAITE POISON TRIAL
